---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Privacy Policy | Real BMI"
    description="Read our privacy policy. Real BMI ensures your health data remains private and is never stored on our servers."
>
    <Navbar />
    <PageShell
      title="Privacy Policy"
      eyebrow="Your data, your privacy"
      description="Learn how Real BMI protects your input data and keeps all calculations private and secure."
      returnUrl="/en"
      returnLabel="Home"
    >
      <div class="space-y-8 prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-[var(--muted-foreground)] leading-relaxed text-lg md:text-xl font-medium opacity-90">
        <p>At <strong>Real BMI</strong>, we take your privacy seriously. Our BMI, BMR, TDEE, and body composition calculators are designed so that your personal inputs remain on your device and never get stored on our servers.</p>

        <h2>What we collect</h2>
        <p>We do not collect, store, or share your height, weight, age, or health inputs. The calculations are performed locally in your browser, making Real BMI a privacy-first health tool.</p>

        <h2>How we use data</h2>
        <p>Only anonymous usage patterns may be collected for product improvement. This helps us refine calculator accuracy, improve user experience, and optimize the site without compromising your personal health information.</p>

        <h2>Third-party services</h2>
        <p>We do not sell or trade your data. Any analytics we use are aggregated and anonymized. We may use standard web services for hosting and performance, but these do not receive your calculator inputs.</p>

        <h2>Security</h2>
        <p>We strive to keep Real BMI secure with modern web practices. If you have questions about privacy or security, contact us and we will respond quickly.</p>
      </div>
    </PageShell>
</Layout>
